SUMMARY:American Fools: The Music of John Mellencamp
DESCRIPTION:Indiana natives saluting the music of John Cougar Mellencamp. Bringing the biggest Hoosier hits and the deepest cuts to the heartland of America. American Fools brings the feel-good groove of John (Cougar) Mellencamp’s songs to life on the stage. We take you on a journey through his career\, including tracks like: Hurts So Good\, Cherry Bomb\, Jack & Diane\, R.O.C.K. in the USA\, I Need A Lover (that won’t drive me crazy)\, Lonely Ol’ Night\, Thundering Hearts\, China Girl\, Crumblin’ Down\, Rain on the Scarecrow\, Pink Houses. \nBUY TICKETS!
